{"tid":1636779,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"國際商業銀行倒閉新聞 (重溫)","createTime":"2019-10-07T21:21:42.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-08T14:57:22.000Z","uid":279401,"like":12,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"3d6916f6da8ee5bfc60d66c2eaf8c24ba27e8b75","tid":1636779,"uid":279401,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T21:21:42.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">1991年7月5日晚，香港的銀監專員發表聲明指，香港的國商銀行財政狀況健全</span></span>（後於1999年證明其言屬實），國商集團的問題發生在香港以外，與香港的國商銀行無關，<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">但事件隨即出現轉變。7月6日，當時的香港銀監會（香港金融管理局前身）發現國商在1988至90年間出現有問題貸款</span></span>，國商銀行大股東阿布扎比政府拒絕向香港國商注資。<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">7月7日晚上，銀監會宣佈，政府已指令香港國商次日凌晨暫停營業</span></span>，隨後，當時的財政司翟克誠（已故）更表示，<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">政府不會動用外匯基金挽救銀行</span></span>，因國商已經於1988至1990年證實出現財務問題，<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">且政府不為國商的無紀錄負債提供擔保，最終導致國商於7月17日清盤。</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/WT3k7gzeikE\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FWT3k7gzeikE&d=wXQbzQ6sjjdDHWUhljjVf9T2hWdA4JmoO%2FtHFZtOkv0%3D&h=4204c201\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/WT3k7gzeikE</a>"},{"pid":"8f8bba80491cf63100a755ddc0c1e9dbb6f0f605","tid":1636779,"uid":228934,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T23:32:10.000Z","msg":"最後點"},{"pid":"c3b494ec3cf74a883b2217f3fa3e5971305cac84","tid":1636779,"uid":279401,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"8f8bba80491cf63100a755ddc0c1e9dbb6f0f605","tid":1636779,"uid":228934,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T23:32:10.000Z","msg":"最後點"},"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-10-08T00:28:38.000Z","msg":"存款只攞返部份，借貸要還足！"},{"pid":"133892fdd5cb0c52391ab5b58f47367082d61097","tid":1636779,"uid":228934,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c3b494ec3cf74a883b2217f